  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Use the exact color tokens provided in the design guidelines. Do not invent new colors.",
    "Implement Cormorant Garamond for all headings. Ensure it is imported via Google Fonts. Use Manrope for body text.",
    "Do NOT use generic card components with heavy shadows. Use flat, clean, minimalistic containers with the specified border color (#E5DED3).",
    "Ensure the header nav has uppercase text with generous letter spacing (tracking-widest).",
    "For the hero section, implement a gradient mask on the left side of the image to blend it smoothly into the background, and overlay the text on the gradient.",
    "Product images should scale up by 1.05 on hover (duration 600ms, ease out). The 'Add to Cart' button should start outlined in gold and fill with solid gold on hover.",
    "All interactive elements must include a data-testid attribute in kebab-case."
  ]
